When car is being externelly locked diagnostics shall NOT be performed on listed in file header diagnostics request.

When diagnostics are reject NRC shall be set to DCM_E_GENERALREJECT.
boolean - TRUE when diagnostics are possible, FALSE if NOT possible

briefdescription.para: Zv diagnostic wrapper to check if diagnostics services are allowed.

detaileddescription.para:
Source
ZvDiagControl.c Revision
version Author
uib05950 Date
Mar 24, 2020 This is to fulfill requirements that we shall reject diagnostics services when car is externally locked. All listed in file diagnostics request goes through addtional check CheckZvDiagAvailable. If car is currently in state externally locked there is NO diagnostics possible to perform and diagnostic shall return value DCM_E_NOT_OK with NRC DCM_E_GENERALREJECT
